Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？听到好大的一下声响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐  寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是大事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贴  我贴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种意外就是会在心急的时候发生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我是在冰箱下面看到了某黑色物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当时吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样差不多就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  谢谢大家帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不必紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就体现出住在学校正对面的好处了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  这个周末准备怎么过？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿玩玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周因为要考试哪都没去成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆去游乐园之类的地方大玩一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去地下卖场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下卖场？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要买什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不买
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始发期末考试成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均分是55分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点低呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25分以下的人是要补考的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的英文语法试题很难的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能达到平均线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我英文语法很不擅长的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}Grammar　　　　　　　　{\r}\n话说  语法到底是什么意思来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}Gram  　{\r}\n是不是克的比较级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gram  grammar  glamourous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glamourous？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  成绩怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考试在昨天就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说还有课要上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心情已经完全进入了春假模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个周末要去哪里逛逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这时  意想不到的事件发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英文语法不及格  下星期补考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里还有心情去玩乐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天由乃亲的Ｘ看上去比平时要大上一号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家都会尽全力帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还留着去年的笔记  来帮你补习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些好吃的给你送去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来为由乃亲 制造游乐园气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  那样只会让我难过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  24分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25分以下是不及格  我正好被卡下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这里是不是批错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确拼错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是22分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月28日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我大吃一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的休息天  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龙面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲要用英文说出这些食材的名称才能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来这么一手？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…Noodle对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Soup  还有Chicken  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼糕是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我开动了）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得语法考试里是不会出现这种问题的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fishcake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在复习什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试已经结束了说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在复习英文语法  因为要补考
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英文语法？老师的英语很棒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Glamourous
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I Love You～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的日式英语发音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  多亏大家帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  为什么英文语法考得那么差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为数学和英文同一天考  我光顾着复习数学了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那数学考得不错罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷子刚刚发下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸飞机？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考得不怎么样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  还有最后一题就全复习完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏大家的帮忙  顺利复习完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的补考  感觉能轻松过关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题：请把下面的句子译为英语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝了这个饮料会感觉很不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃她不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哇…Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖～乖～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贴  我贴  我贴贴贴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  不过是补考啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也很厉害了  因为全答对了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  晚饭做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃做了什么料理？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞汤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Stew念错了。）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炖汤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Potato  carrot  onion  broccoli  chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flour  bulbar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  够了  已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  一聊就回想起了好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲做的炖汤  超美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考试不想再挂红灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园  下次再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都能收租金了哪～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在扫走廊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不赖真不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有什么事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来打扫空房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的新生就快要入住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…是和我们不同的一年级生…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样哦  二年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空房间就快要搬进一年新生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是大新闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说暖阳庄就快住满人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说暖阳庄就快沉入地下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:36.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一词多义，宫子太兴奋导致寻理解错误。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搬进两个一年级生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要住满了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么说啊  都时隔三年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违的滋润的小日子就快回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将发泡酒升级成啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（发泡酒是一种使用辅料高达75%以上的带有气泡的酒类。\n其口感外观与普通啤酒相似，但成本低，相比啤酒更便宜。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都能喝上喜欢的白薯烧酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连平时舍不得喝的Dom Perignon酒都有幸一尝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Dom Perignon是Mo?t et Chandon公司所生产的香槟的品牌。）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有空的话帮我一起打扫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请人的话会很贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好脏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间没人用的话居然能脏成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级生啊  会是什么样的孩子们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如长得比我还高点的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这点是肯定不会错的啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着空空如也的房间就想起了自己搬过来时的情形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在我第一次见到沙英的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有些难以相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么特别的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能一点感想都没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:14:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那可能吧～不可能的吧～说说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像糖人点心似的的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好～外卖来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英  把楼上那俩孩子叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是房东叫来的外卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是帮忙打扫的谢礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烤猪排便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡肉南蛮煮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧汁肉排便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂炒蔬菜便当以及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉特别餐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选自己喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  这就是挑剩下的了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  暖阳庄内的网线已经接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想上网的话和我说声就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网线？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  住103的孩子拜托我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有电脑的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖阳庄终于也要进行IT革命了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子  知道IT革命是什么的缩写吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In～ternet！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听说暖阳庄的大新闻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两个一年级生要入住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我也很喜欢迎接新人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正忙着做准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  那是用来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…房东  一年级生哪一天搬过来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都是后天下午过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天…明天一天做点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画新生的想像画像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月3日  ‘欢迎来到暖阳庄’
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  感到紧张吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微有点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么样的女孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能相处得好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前由乃亲来这里时的情景还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  最紧张的还是一年级生她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打起精神来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗了澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但才刚过9点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  也不用特地去迎接她们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  各位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好  今后请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸箱全部放在这里可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的工作就到此为止了  就此拜别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就弄好了  离那孩子来还有段时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  大家一起去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（鸦雀无声…）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  谁都不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好饱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到突然就被拖去吃饭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有这样开朗的父母不也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:20:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的就是那对夫妻的孩子和搞IT革命的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么样的女孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去准备好茶水等她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是一团乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想迎接她们的却被她们迎接了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能好好相处就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉和小荠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好  是暖阳庄的各位…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:20:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经到这里了啊  代我们向你的父母问好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚和他们一起吃了饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺水推舟地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫荠  刚搬到203室来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是新生吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有同龄人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做乃莉  住103室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是201室的由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,202室的宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃和宫子是二年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是三年级生  我叫沙英  住102室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是寻  多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正巧要搬行李
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些手忙脚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等安定下来了来我家喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的话大家一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等下就去您那里拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等你们～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:22:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生活稳定之前如果有什么需要的话尽管开口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后就多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月3日  ‘完’  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你们暖阳庄的三个优势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  离学校很近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二  光照良好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住得舒适也是个优势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的两位觉得如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还不是很清楚  但和大家在一起很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘4月6日～7日  YES  NO’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘7月19日  Olive’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在暖阳庄里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来看哦
